snippet.title: Age of Water — Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist us! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2695490

The second phase of the closed beta test is live! To be guaranteed taking part in the test, you can buy one of the Early Access kits. Also, some of the players that applied for the free trial on the official site, will be also invited to the test.
